task.summary: Added basic DAO implementations (Still needs the functionality)

MovementDTS added the basic connection classes for synchronized request reply. ClientConnection can now be used as a base for the other systems to extend and use RemoteCall to get a reply to their queries.
Also created the basic reply connection and server connection that serves as a base for the server to be able to process and answer queries via reflection.
